social_posts.post_text: Quick flight to Texas to pick up my new rig

Another item off the checklist. Renewed my MRC pro license as well as credentials. We’ll be running #328 again for Coastal Moto/Zeigler Motorsports. 

Now to finalize some more sponsors for 7-9 rounds of Pro Racing. 🫡🫡
Just needs some #328 logos for round 2 of the MRC Atlantic Series, big thanks to Triple S Cycle Works for the support and Coastal Moto!
Pretty stoked to have some fresh @teamevs fusion socks! They go hand in hand with my Axis Sport braces. Big thanks to y’all! @rdenotto 💪🏻
Big thanks too  In De-Fence Riders for letting us ride tonight. Next ride day is Thursday after 5!

Some Red Line Synthetic Oil goodies arrived in a pallet yesterday. Had to snap some pictures 💪🏻 

Big thanks goes to them for their continued support of my program! 🫡👌
Mark Beatty

I’m going to try something a little new. I am  seeking sponsorship for 3 Canadian nationals. 

Gopher Dunes National- July 9th
MX 101 Sand Del Lee National- July 16th
Motocross Deschambault- July 30th

Sponsorship levels vary and I have a program for your budget!

Company/individual would get a spot on my bike and helmet and autographed poster. 

Anything higher than $500 would get a logo on bike, helmet, autographed poster, and a signed jersey! 

You can DM me or email me at talanhansenracing@yahoo.com
